<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Cadastro - My Social</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="img/favicon-32x32.png" type="image/png" sizes="32x32">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/materialize.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/animate.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <section class="mySocial">
        <img class="mySocial-background" src="img/bg.jpg" alt="My Social">
        
        <div class="mySocial-container">
            <div class="mySocial-logo">
                <img src="img/logo.png" alt="My Social logo">
            </div>
            <div class="mySocial-paragrafos">
                <p class="mySocial-paragrafoMylogo">My logo</p><p class="mySocial-paragrafoSocial">Social</p> 
            </div>      
           <div class="mySocial-animate">
                <h1>Olá Mundo!</h1> 
                <p>
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Pellentesque sed est a elit imperdiet blandit. 
                Mauris ac fringilla nunc. Maecenas eu tellus non lacus pharetra venenatis eu quis dolor.
                Donec lacinia, leo vitae egestas accumsan, ipsum elit lacinia purus, non ullamcorper nisi nunc nec ipsum. 
                </p> 
                <button class="" type="button">Leia mais</button>       
           </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mySocial-coluna2 container">
            <div class="row">
                    <form class="col s11" action="/dashboard" method="post">
                       <h1 class="titulo">Cadastro</h1>
                            <div class="input-field">
                                <input id="nome" name="nome" type="text" class="validate">
                                <label for="nome">Nome completo</label>
                                <span></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="input-field">
                                <input id="email" name="email" type="email" class="validate">
                                <label for="email">Email</label>
                                <span></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="input-field">
                                <input id="senha" name="senha" type="password" class="validate">
                                <label for="senha">Senha</label>
                                <span></span>
                            </div>
                             <div class="input-field">
                                <input id="confimacao_senha" name="confimacao_senha" type="password" class="validate">
                                <label for="confimacao_senha">Confirme sua senha</label>
                                <span></span>
                            </div>
                            <input type="submit" class="mySocial-coluna2-btn-entrar" value="Entrar">
                            
                            <p>Já possui uma conta?<a href="/login" class="mySocial-coluna2-login">Login</a></p> 
                            
                    </form>
                </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <script src="js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/materializa.min.js"s></script>
     <script>
        $(document).ready(function(){
            $('.mySocial-animate').addClass('animated slideInLeft');
            $('.mySocial-coluna2').addClass('animated fadeInDown');
        }); 
    </script>
</body>
</html>
